panels.name: Most Attacked URLs
panels.queryString: pri outcome | parse "request=* requestMethod=*" as url, other | parse field=other "app=* outcome" as app | count by url, app | top 10 url, app by _count | transpose row app column url

panels.name: This month
panels.queryString: pri outcome | parse "app=* outcome" as app | count_distinct(app)

panels.name: Attacks by outcome
panels.queryString:
pri outcome 
| parse "pri=* src=*" as attack, other 
| parse field=other "app=* outcome=*" as app, outcome
| count by attack, app, outcome | sort by attack

panels.name: Attacks by Type and URL
panels.queryString:
pri outcome 
| parse "pri=* src=*" as attack, other 
| parse field=other "request=* requestMethod=* app=* outcome" as url, requestMethod, app
| count by attack, url, app | sort by url

panels.name: Attacks by Type
panels.queryString: pri outcome | parse "pri=* src=*" as attack, other | parse field=other "app=* outcome" as app | count by attack, app | transpose row app column attack

panels.name: Today
panels.queryString: pri outcome | parse "app=* outcome" as app | count_distinct(app)

panels.name: This week
panels.queryString: pri outcome | parse "app=* outcome" as app | count_distinct(app)
